New York Mets to Put Third Baseman David Wright on Disabled List Tomorrow

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-05-17T22:37:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/new-york-mets-to-put-third-baseman-david-wright-on-disabled-list-tomorrow.html
The  New York Mets  will place third
baseman  David Wright  on the 15-day disabled list tomorrow with a
lower back stress fracture, the team said today in a news
release.  Wright, 28, who is hitting .226 in 39 games this season,
has not played since May 15. He will be replaced on the roster
by infielder Nick Evans, who will be promoted from the Metsâ€™
